    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has some visible scratches and minor dings, and the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it will eventually need some routine maintenance and minor repairs to reach peak performance. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and a few projects to tackle.",
